description.value:
**Plugin Pack to monitor Azure Cosmos DB Account service using RestAPI or AZCLI.**

Available Host template and related Services:

|Cloud-Azure-Database-CosmosDb-custom|
|---|
|Availability|
|Cache|
|Document|
|Health|
|Latency|
|Throughput|
|Units|
|Usage|

This Plugin-Pack provides a Host discovery *provider* to be used with the Host discovery module.

**Plugin Pack pour superviser les ressources Azure Cosmos DB Account via RestAPI ou AZCLI.**

Modèle d\'Hôte disponible et Services associés:

|Cloud-Azure-Database-CosmosDb-custom|
|---|
|Availability|
|Cache|
|Document|
|Health|
|Latency|
|Throughput|
|Units|
|Usage|

Ce Plugin-Pack fournit un *provider* Host Discovery pour le module d\'auto-découverte d\'Hôtes
